# Backtesting & Walk-Forward Validation Framework

## What This Skill Covers
The full pipeline from raw historical data → strategy simulation → performance metrics → walk-forward validation → go/no-go decision. This framework is the ground truth for whether a strategy has edge before it touches real money.

## Data Requirements
```python
# Minimum data needed before backtesting
MIN_CANDLES          = 2000       # ~20 days of 15min BTC candles
RECOMMENDED_CANDLES  = 17520      # 6 months of 15min data
IDEAL_CANDLES        = 35040      # 12 months = sees multiple regimes

# Required fields per candle
candle = {
    "timestamp": ...,   # Unix ms
    "open": ...,
    "high": ...,
    "low": ...,
    "close": ...,
    "volume": ...,
}

# Required for OBI backtesting (harder to get historically)
order_book_snapshot = {
